You are implementing new Angular components for the DesignFlow Item Library page redesign. Write the files exactly as specified below. All components are `standalone: false` (NgModule pattern). Do NOT add unit test files. Do NOT add comments explaining what you're doing.

Working directory: `C:\repos\dflow\designflow-frontend`

