## Design tokens (CSS custom properties for reference)
```
--ink: #1c1b22   --ink-2: #46454f   --ink-3: #76747f   --ink-4: #a8a6af
--line: #e7e3dd  --line-2: #f0ece6  --paper: #ffffff   --bg: #f5f3ef   --chip: #f1eee9
