--accent: #c2662f --accent-700: #9a4f23 --accent-50: #f7ece2
```

## Status → tone mapping
```
concept    → bg:#f1eee9 / fg:#46454f / dot:#76747f
in design  → bg:#ecebf6 / fg:#302e63 / dot:#3f3d86
submitted  → bg:#f7efe0 / fg:#8a6312 / dot:#c08a2a
approved   → bg:#e8f1ea / fg:#2f6a45 / dot:#3f8a5b
in sampling→ bg:#f7ece2 / fg:#9a4f23 / dot:#c2662f
production → bg:#ecebf6 / fg:#302e63 / dot:#3f3d86
on shelf   → bg:#e8f1ea / fg:#2f6a45 / dot:#3f8a5b
discontinued→bg:#f7e7e4 / fg:#9a3a30 / dot:#bd5246
```

## Helper function (use in every component that needs it)
```typescript
function stringToHue(str: string): number {
  let hash = 0;
  for (let i = 0; i < str.length; i++) {
    hash = str.charCodeAt(i) + ((hash << 5) - hash);
  }
  return Math.abs(hash) % 360;
}
```

