## FILE 4: `src/app/pages/itemLibrary/status-pill/status-pill.component.ts`

AG-Grid cell renderer. Selector `app-status-pill`.

Define interface `PillTone { bg: string; fg: string; dot: string }`.

Map constant `STATUS_TONES: Record<string, PillTone>` with keys: `concept, design, submitted, approved, sampling, production, shelf, discont` (see tone mapping above).

Map constant `STATUS_KEY_MAP: Record<string, string>` mapping lowercase status labels to stage keys:
- `'concept'→'concept'`, `'in design'→'design'`, `'submitted'→'submitted'`, `'approved'→'approved'`, `'in sampling'→'sampling'`, `'production'→'production'`, `'on shelf'→'shelf'`, `'discontinued'→'discont'`

Properties: `label = ''`, `tone: PillTone = STATUS_TONES['concept']`.

`agInit` + `refresh`: set `label = String(params.value || '')`, look up tone via `STATUS_KEY_MAP[label.toLowerCase().trim()]` → fallback to `'concept'`.

