## FILE 10: `src/app/pages/itemLibrary/split-rail/split-rail.component.ts`

Selector `app-split-rail`. NOT a cell renderer — a regular Angular component.

Inputs: `@Input() item: any`, `@Input() imgSrc: string | null = null`.
Output: none needed.

Inject: `Router` from `@angular/router`.

Properties:
- `fields: Array<{label: string; value: string; mono?: boolean; full?: boolean}> = []`
- `statusLabel = ''`
- `statusTone = { bg: '#f1eee9', fg: '#46454f', dot: '#76747f' }`
- Same STATUS_TONES and STATUS_KEY_MAP constants as status-pill (copy them in)

On `set item(val)`:
- Store `_item = val`
- Call `buildFields()`

`buildFields()`:
- If no item, clear fields/status and return
- Build `statusLabel = item.status || ''`
- Look up `statusTone` from STATUS_TONES via STATUS_KEY_MAP
- Build `fields` array:
  ```
  { label: 'Item Num',    value: item.itemNum || '—', mono: true }
  { label: 'Reference #', value: item.refNum || '—',  mono: true }
  { label: 'Design #',    value: item.DSN || '—',     mono: true }
  { label: 'Season',      value: item.season || '—',  mono: true }
  { label: 'Licensor',    value: item.licensorName || item.licensor || '—', full: true }
  { label: 'Product Type',  value: item.materialName  || item.material  || '—' }
  { label: 'Sub-Type',      value: item.constructionName || item.construction || '—' }
  { label: 'Feature',       value: item.featureName   || item.feature   || '—' }
  { label: 'Size',          value: item.sizeName      || item.size      || '—', mono: true }
  { label: 'Division',      value: String(item.div_code_fk || '—') }
  ```

`onOpen()`: if `_item?.id` call `router.navigate(['/apps/itemDetail/' + _item.id])`.

`get itemName()`: return `_item?.item_name || _item?.name || ''`.
`get itemMeta()`: return `[_item?.propertyName || _item?.property, _item?.materialName || _item?.material].filter(Boolean).join(' · ')`.

Also expose `_item` as private, `hasItem` getter (`!!_item`).

